\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愈黎愈覺得自己好撚廢。<br />\n<br />\n果位親人走左之後又控制唔倒自己情緒，成日男人老狗一個人起屋企會突然間喊到停唔撚倒好似癲左咁，有幾次無啦啦行街搭車都忍唔倒喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩冇俾人望倒，真係好on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"除左運動之外 巴打會唔會有其他興趣啊 ？<br />\n我覺得有啲野忙可以避免自己成日諗返起之前 <br />\n同埋專注一樣野都可以有種進步緊既感覺 ！！<br />\n<br />\n另外 我覺得其實世界上好多毒撚同我地一樣<br />\n不過佢地太毒 所以發現唔到佢地 <br />\n所以巴打唔係自己一個架 <br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇下 我覺得幾得意 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ted.com/talks/susan_cain_the_power_of_introverts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Fsusan_cain_the_power_of_introverts&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=858a5722\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ted.com/talks/susan_cain_the_power_of_introverts</a>"},{"pid":"ce3622f94db8e6d86dfb3e488a4aea5269089d39","tid":1054031,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"點解要救 其實應該享受<br />\n同人相處覺得好麻煩 有時自己想去邊就去邊做咩就做咩幾好呀"},{"pid":"fd17798b3c3f99cf27858a324f359ff97a4f10f0","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a08808a7f9641feb960af9c87ef65820554c7ea","tid":1054031,"uid":56146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa5267c9bcfe678cc92bd46d400085c8dbe68e7a","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d90cd11c45e0b711374efcc340b544ddce1dd46","tid":1054031,"uid":56146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:11:53.000Z","msg":"冇人覆你我覆，同你差唔多，冇乜fd搵，冇女，同事放工唔會聯絡，好彩兩老健在，已慣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"我諗我係要學識去面對一個人既生活，多過逼自己去social又或者識人之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終依啲野強求唔黎<br />\n<br />\n但有時一個人自己都覺得好悶，衰在夜晚鳩痕上黎又真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前打完J就瞓倒，宜家打完J都覺得出唔倒火，想轉移精力出去做運動又整撚親左隻腳，仆街有排都好唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愈黎愈覺得自己好撚廢。<br />\n<br />\n果位親人走左之後又控制唔倒自己情緒，成日男人老狗一個人起屋企會突然間喊到停唔撚倒好似癲左咁，有幾次無啦啦行街搭車都忍唔倒喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩冇俾人望倒，真係好on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:17:19.000Z","msg":"跑步好撚悶，個人就唔鍾意跑。不過跑過10k，完成咗又幾開心。做吓gym都好，只要唔好怕第一次去，做做吓就唔怕比人望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"以前去過次gym玩跑步機，俾隔離班友臭到我跑一步都即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚憎人地啲臭汗味，寧願出街跑或者留起屋企做避開人地，但街路唔平又跑到隻腳收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又唔想成日做重訓，練完會更加想打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打左出黎又會勁攰，唔打又好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天就話有得游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />游冬泳真係唔得。之前想試下行返山，但腳痛天勉強唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變左冇咩運動可以做，收工龜縮起屋企打機"},{"pid":"caee51ead512efbe4dbfa2f8f78d6ff8cce47bb7","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eadeb3733e0aa32cc93b21a38d4bdf3c0eefdbd","tid":1054031,"uid":165017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa5267c9bcfe678cc92bd46d400085c8dbe68e7a","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d90cd11c45e0b711374efcc340b544ddce1dd46","tid":1054031,"uid":56146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:11:53.000Z","msg":"冇人覆你我覆，同你差唔多，冇乜fd搵，冇女，同事放工唔會聯絡，好彩兩老健在，已慣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"我諗我係要學識去面對一個人既生活，多過逼自己去social又或者識人之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終依啲野強求唔黎<br />\n<br />\n但有時一個人自己都覺得好悶，衰在夜晚鳩痕上黎又真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前打完J就瞓倒，宜家打完J都覺得出唔倒火，想轉移精力出去做運動又整撚親左隻腳，仆街有排都好唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愈黎愈覺得自己好撚廢。<br />\n<br />\n果位親人走左之後又控制唔倒自己情緒，成日男人老狗一個人起屋企會突然間喊到停唔撚倒好似癲左咁，有幾次無啦啦行街搭車都忍唔倒喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩冇俾人望倒，真係好on9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"除左運動之外 巴打會唔會有其他興趣啊 ？<br />\n我覺得有啲野忙可以避免自己成日諗返起之前 <br />\n同埋專注一樣野都可以有種進步緊既感覺 ！！<br />\n<br />\n另外 我覺得其實世界上好多毒撚同我地一樣<br />\n不過佢地太毒 所以發現唔到佢地 <br />\n所以巴打唔係自己一個架 <br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇下 我覺得幾得意 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ted.com/talks/susan_cain_the_power_of_introverts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ted.com%2Ftalks%2Fsusan_cain_the_power_of_introverts&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=858a5722\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ted.com/talks/susan_cain_the_power_of_introverts</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:06:10.000Z","msg":"睇過依條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前讀U果陣好得閒，會成日諗好多依啲野去暸解自己既處境，最尾發覺會諗到壞腦，又改善唔倒咩野，所以算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但出黎做野之後有好多問題冇得唔面對，成個人就開始好焦慮，個心態好唔安定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔想屋企人擔心<br />\n<br />\n原本幾鐘意影相同埋玩下耳機野，但一黎冇咁多錢燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />二黎份人唔知幾時變得好自卑，唔想影自己，去旅行都唔想同人影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />影完好多風景相都唔會去執相睇返<br />\n<br />\n有諗過研究下佛學啲野，但又好似冇咩依方面既緣份，自己睇完都係唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔想搵人交流<br />\n<br />\n宜家睇緊有冇機會進修同順便r張master沙紙，但轉個頭諗，屌讀左咁撚多年書已經好撚攰，仲要逼自己收工再踩返落個坑到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又唔似果班叻既毒撚咁自修日文N1，冇咁既目標同熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日收工覺得自己成條鹹魚咁<br />\n<br />\n之前果排就係一收工就起勢去跑。一路睇風景追住日落跑真係好開心好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果冇整親隻腳既話。"},{"pid":"4c80afdcb05fc63713b944625032ec3b38c93941","tid":1054031,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a4161d3a97bfe2d9e14c2612e43d20a4ae8aa2","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce3622f94db8e6d86dfb3e488a4aea5269089d39","tid":1054031,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"點解要救 其實應該享受<br />\n同人相處覺得好麻煩 有時自己想去邊就去邊做咩就做咩幾好呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:10:01.000Z","msg":"或者我係想搵返以前果種安心咁生活既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由細到大都係一個人咁捱架啦，點樣宜家會諗得咁多同咁唔定。"},{"pid":"815c8dad1cdbc2b090515f9cb9501e573bdaea27","tid":1054031,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過養吓狗/貓"},{"pid":"4bf1d20cb283209414cf351a8f7c590c2bc0aed9","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815c8dad1cdbc2b090515f9cb9501e573bdaea27","tid":1054031,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過養吓狗/貓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"好想養貓但同緊屋企人住又唔養得住。一黎未有能力搬出去一個人住，二黎唔知自己處理倒唔倒寵物依件事。有時去下貓cafe或者街貓黎撩我我反而唔知點相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂多撚佢兩下咁"},{"pid":"3e98faa078eee9a947070ceb41f51f87a4c11396","tid":1054031,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf1d20cb283209414cf351a8f7c590c2bc0aed9","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815c8dad1cdbc2b090515f9cb9501e573bdaea27","tid":1054031,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過養吓狗/貓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"好想養貓但同緊屋企人住又唔養得住。一黎未有能力搬出去一個人住，二黎唔知自己處理倒唔倒寵物依件事。有時去下貓cafe或者街貓黎撩我我反而唔知點相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂多撚佢兩下咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"如果你同緊屋企人住已經覺得孤獨，咁勸你唔好自己一個住，驚你有抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n如果有小動物淨係撚佢幾吓都覺得好開心，佢嗲一嗲你又會覺得好溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望你有機會就養吓"},{"pid":"4f59d5350e2d4cef018cba72ef71dacfe5a31d73","tid":1054031,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9706128f026a8beb4222ef22a887913ed43157df","tid":1054031,"uid":203237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:34:26.000Z","msg":"巴打自己有冇啲咩興趣噤？"},{"pid":"16d5696d13ba8176baaa33d1e21e25b834198684","tid":1054031,"uid":125864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇諗過打開自己識多啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f363bf3173f9dc3de2b0f44b7f7bcaad99ce76","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9706128f026a8beb4222ef22a887913ed43157df","tid":1054031,"uid":203237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T18:34:26.000Z","msg":"巴打自己有冇啲咩興趣噤？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"前面講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係諗唔倒仲有咩興趣，格硬再搵就唯有講睇書囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前會特登出中央圖書館同濕鳩cafe度搵下書hea下，突然有一排唔想再掂書，同埋覺得件事有啲on99就算數。<br />\n<br />\n其實以前定下心留起屋企可以衰瞇書追成套小說，但真係做唔返件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多書未開就擺撚晒起床底封塵，遲下想放晒佢算，唔會想睇"},{"pid":"594463a06bb7446454fb148bc81251d0fa9c8fd3","tid":1054031,"uid":241448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16d5696d13ba8176baaa33d1e21e25b834198684","tid":1054031,"uid":125864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇諗過打開自己識多啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"價值觀好難改，成日覺得以前自己係衰啲on99既野俾人欺凌，我就會諗點樣搵同改自己既on9位去同人相處，好在意其他人會唔會突然好似以前果啲中學班垃圾咁玩鳩你，同埋敏感到成撚日懷疑人地諗緊自己有乜地方衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟本被害妄想症，明明冇人咁再對待自己，又要成日起度提醒自己咪撚做on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學前面果位師兄話齋，將自己同其他人諗得太重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出黎做野之後雖然多左圈子，但又覺得同周圍所有人唔夾，逼自己去埋堆結果又好撚唔開心覺得好晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即使最close果啲fd都係間唔中先會wts傾同約出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab5be2683466f352619dbb32df61af1eee43651","tid":1054031,"uid":1108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"同樓主差唔多 有被欺凌經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對於人呢樣野都睇到化哂 唔信D咩人際關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得一兩個中同間唔時傾下計食下飯。<br />\n<br />\n由中學識事開始 已經開始咩都靠自己 做個自私嘅獨行者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出到黎做野更加係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d0b739973e864a94d33f6810f0052f58f72daf","tid":1054031,"uid":168551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594463a06bb7446454fb148bc81251d0fa9c8fd3","ti